case class LineInfo(filePath: String, extension: String, line: Int,  nLines: Int, nBytes: Int, text: String)

def lineInfo(s: String): LineInfo = {
    val p = s.indexOf('>')
    val infoPart = s.substring(0, p)
    val text = s.substring(p + 1)
    val info = infoPart.split(":")
    val dot = info(0).lastIndexOf('.')
    val extension = info(0).substring(dot+1)
    LineInfo(info(0), extension, info(1).toInt, info(2).toInt, info(3).toInt, text)
}
